♪Become who I am♪

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,260
[Wild Ambition Bloom]

29
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from Stone and Water's novel,
The Uncaged Flame]

30
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 34]

31
00:01:58,790 --> 00:01:59,460
You're home?

32
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:03,770
What's wrong?

33
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,980
Too much stress
preparing for the wedding?

34
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:18,260
Do you know exactly how Xia Chu died?

35
00:02:22,470 --> 00:02:23,850
Why bring this up now?

36
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:28,500
I need to know the truth.

37
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:37,010
The truth is,

38
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:40,660
Mu Ziru killed him.

39
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,730
But the real culprit was the KMT.

40
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,410
Five years ago,

41
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:52,570
the person who called Xia Chu away
while he was trying on his suit

42
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,410
was you.

43
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,170
What exactly did you tell him?

44
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,260
He rushed off

45
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,340
without even saying goodbye.

46
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,660
Who told you all this?

47
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,730
For five years,

48
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,610
why didn't you ever say a word
about this?

49
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,380
What are you hiding?

50
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,500
What are you so afraid of?

51
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,290
This note was found

52
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,890
on Xia Chu.

53
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,410
This is your handwriting, isn't it?

54
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:13,010
Why was your note on Xia Chu?

55
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,340
Why did you tell him
to pick up the medicine?

56
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:32,140
Mu Ziru told me himself

57
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,140
they went to Kangning Clinic

58
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,610
to arrest someone else.

59
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,900
But when they got there,

60
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,810
they found Xia Chu too.

61
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:46,700
So this note

62
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:51,540
was the reason Xia Chu was there, right?

63
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,370
What's your relationship with Lingdang?

64
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,900
He's a patient. Nothing more.

65
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:17,810
Without an inside man,

66
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,930
we couldn't have taken out Mu Ziru.

67
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,700
So that was Lingdang, right?

68
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,850
I figured as much.

69
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:33,100
He also benefited from Mu Ziru's death.

70
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,540
Lingdang was

71
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:39,900
part of Xia Chu's death, wasn't he?

72
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,490
You sure know how to spin a story.

73
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,460
Spin a story?

74
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:55,250
Then tell me,

75
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,930
on the morning of April 12, 1927,

76
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:01,140
Lingdang showed up

77
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:03,700
just as Wen's Pharmacy opened.

78
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,050
What was he doing there?

79
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,580
He was just here to get some medicine.

80
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:07,610
Really?

81
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,540
For whom?

82
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:11,780
For his mother.

83
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,490
His mother committed suicide by drowning

84
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,850
twenty years ago.

85
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,340
Is that so? I didn't know.

86
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,170
Really?

87
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:20,610
I'll say it for you.

88
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:24,540
He wanted to tell you

89
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:27,980
he was heading to Kangning Clinic

90
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:30,020
to arrest CPC members, didn't he?

91
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,540
After that,

92
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:35,290
you went
to the Western-style tailor shop,

93
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,610
found Xia Chu,

94
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,370
and told him to pick up the medicine.

95
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,540
So Xia Chu went

96
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:46,900
straight to Kangning Clinic.

97
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:49,980
There, he ran into Mu Ziru.

98
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:54,170
And just like that,
Mu Ziru shot him dead.

99
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,020
And you

100
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,930
walked away without a scratch.

101
00:06:58,430 --> 00:06:59,410
Five years later...

102
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,660
I got to marry you.

103
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:06,780
Yes.

104
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,140
So everything I said is true, isn't it?

105
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:16,170
Tell me, was I wrong about any of it?

106
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:19,700
No.

107
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:39,940
♪Draped in the long night's bitter snow♪

108
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:45,070
♪Where lies the final destination?
Looking up, is it heaven or the abyss?♪

109
00:07:45,070 --> 00:07:46,580
You actually admitted it?

110
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,410
Why wouldn't I?

111
00:07:50,410 --> 00:07:52,100
♪The night watchman
with his lamp is gone♪

112
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,050
I can't wash my hands

113
00:07:55,050 --> 00:07:56,680
♪The light I followed
was but a firefly's deceit♪

114
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,900
of Xia Chu's death.

115
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:05,180
♪Who judges right from wrong,
and who breaks the judge's gavel?♪

116
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:11,800
♪If faith collapses,
where do answers lie?♪

117
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:14,050
Aren't you going to defend yourself?

118
00:08:14,050 --> 00:08:17,120
♪Black and white entwined,
day and night reversed♪

119
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,460
What's there to defend?

120
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,830
♪The flame within my heart
can only blaze when fed with tears♪

121
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,850
Why you?

122
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,420
Why?

123
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,380
Why would you do this to me?

124
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:26,260
Pull the trigger!

125
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:28,900
♪Heaven and Earth shatter,
awaiting fire's final breach♪

126
00:08:28,900 --> 00:08:29,620
You're hesitating.

127
00:08:30,260 --> 00:08:31,740
Is doubt holding you back?

128
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:35,460
Or are you still holding on to me?

129
00:08:36,540 --> 00:08:37,180
Do it.

130
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:41,660
♪Dust of the night
shields the future from decay♪

131
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:56,220
♪Through cages woven with broken towers♪

132
00:08:56,700 --> 00:09:04,420
♪How many eyes of greed
lurk in the shade?♪

133
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:08,420
♪Draining the sun's last glow♪

134
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:11,420
♪On crumbled peaks,
will dawn break anew?♪

135
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:12,180
Wen Zhiqiu.

136
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:16,860
As of today,

137
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:18,900
