awaiting fire's final breach♪

143
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:53,860
♪Dust of the night
shields the future from decay♪

144
00:10:06,820 --> 00:10:07,900
You've had enough to drink.

145
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:10,900
What happened?

146
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:12,340
Don't ask.

147
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:14,220
I don't even know how to explain it.

148
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:16,940
Wen Zhiqiu and I

149
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:19,420
