151
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:33,220
I'll go find him.

152
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:34,180
Don't.

153
00:10:35,260 --> 00:10:35,900
Erniu,

154
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:41,580
there are some things

155
00:10:42,780 --> 00:10:45,860
you couldn't imagine.

156
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:49,380
I'll tell you later.

157
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:52,820
Alright.

158
00:10:59,180 --> 00:11:00,180
Are you okay?

159
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:03,780
I'm fine.

160
00:11:07,180 --> 00:11:08,820
It's just that I met the wrong person.

161
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:18,500
Is this our fate?

162
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:21,260
No.

163
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:25,100
It won't be.

164
00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:26,980
Mr. Wen,

165
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:28,900
Miss Chu just sent someone with a letter

166
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:29,900
and a set of keys.

167
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,220
Leave them here.

168
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:32,740
Okay.

169
00:11:34,140 --> 00:11:35,020
[Resignation]

170
00:11:35,580 --> 00:11:36,220
Mr. Wen,

171
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:37,580
there are rumors
going around the company

172
00:11:37,580 --> 00:11:39,100
that Miss Chu is planning to resign

173
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:40,660
and leave the company for good.

174
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:41,700
Maybe the two of you should

175
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,180
clear things up.

176
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:44,300
No need.

177
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:48,620
