182
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,420
my wife and I fight a lot too.

183
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:07,620
Usually, after a few days, we'd...

184
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:08,860
Enough.

185
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:10,060
Get back to work.

186
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,460
It seems Shaohua heard something

187
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:27,500
before the wedding,

188
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:29,500
so she decided not to get married.

189
00:12:31,620 --> 00:12:33,740
