Time really flies.

356
00:20:29,620 --> 00:20:30,420
How have you been since you got back?

357
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:31,420
Pretty well.

358
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:42,980
How about her?

359
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:44,740
Not so well.

360
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:49,660
What exactly happened between you two?

361
00:20:56,580 --> 00:20:57,820
Is there anything I can do for you?

362
