376
00:21:36,180 --> 00:21:36,980
for you.

377
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:38,300
Tell me.

378
00:21:39,060 --> 00:21:40,260
If she runs into any trouble,

379
00:21:40,260 --> 00:21:41,220
