385
00:22:03,380 --> 00:22:03,940
Thank you.

386
00:22:06,140 --> 00:22:07,700
How much do you need? I'll cover it.

387
00:22:08,020 --> 00:22:09,380
I can't take your money.

388
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:10,860
Why not?

389
00:22:13,140 --> 00:22:14,660
I know things haven't been easy for you.

390
00:22:15,740 --> 00:22:16,900
Your restaurant was bombed

391
00:22:17,140 --> 00:22:18,740
