were wiped out, weren't they?

392
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:21,020
That bit of money you have

393
00:22:21,020 --> 00:22:22,820
won't even make a dent in what I need.

394
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,300
You should hold on to it.

395
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:27,660
Alright.

396
00:22:32,380 --> 00:22:32,980
By the way,

397
00:22:35,060 --> 00:22:37,660
