408
00:23:15,220 --> 00:23:17,820
I know what I'm doing.

409
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:20,380
Erniu, I think...

410
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:21,500
Don't worry.

411
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:24,100
I know what I want,

412
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:25,500
and I will get it.

413
00:23:25,660 --> 00:23:26,340
Money?

414
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,020
Didn't you say

415
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:31,260
you wanted to make your own money?

416
00:23:31,980 --> 00:23:34,100
That's exactly why

417
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:36,180
I need to be with Xia Yuan.

418
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:37,860
I want to learn
how to do business from him.

419
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:39,980
Why don't you

420
00:23:39,980 --> 00:23:41,260
just follow me instead?

421
00:23:41,380 --> 00:23:42,940
I knew you'd say that.

422
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:44,220
