430
00:23:57,260 --> 00:23:57,980
Funny thing is,

431
00:23:58,860 --> 00:24:00,380
I'm the kind of woman

432
00:24:00,380 --> 00:24:02,060
who'd do the same.

433
00:24:02,860 --> 00:24:03,620
Besides,

434
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:05,900
I'm already this messed up.

435
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:08,060
