437
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:12,420
aren't you paying a higher price

438
00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:14,820
for this relationship

439
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:15,740
than any of your others?

440
00:24:17,780 --> 00:24:18,700
This time,

441
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:21,860
I'll walk away
with more than I ever have.

442
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:28,100
There's someone you need to see.

443
00:24:28,380 --> 00:24:29,020
Who?

444
00:24:29,820 --> 00:24:30,420
Coming through.

445
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:42,340
I heard she got all her savings

446
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:44,060
swindled away.

447
00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:47,020
She couldn't keep her hands to herself,

448
00:24:47,780 --> 00:24:49,100
so Mr. Tian threw her out.

449
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:51,620
She then started a small business

450
00:24:52,580 --> 00:24:53,420
and just lost it all again.

451
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:06,660
Thank you.

452
00:25:15,020 --> 00:25:17,260
Bao, I've got some money.

453
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:19,780
How about I send you overseas
for school?

454
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:22,620
Shaozhong,

455
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:24,580
we've earned a bit.

456
00:25:25,620 --> 00:25:27,300
Let's treat ourselves
to some pig's head meat

457
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:28,420
