467
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:42,380
I extend my congratulations
to Ms. Chu Shaohua,

468
00:26:42,580 --> 00:26:44,900
Chairwoman
of Chichun Apothecary Co., Ltd.

469
00:26:45,020 --> 00:26:45,940
and Director of Shaohua Pharmaceuticals.

470
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:49,020
- Good!
- Great!

471
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,620
I'm so thrilled for you.

472
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:52,540
Congratulations.

473
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:54,140
You've finally made your dream
come true.

474
00:26:54,500 --> 00:26:55,620
Honestly, I couldn't be happier.

