00:26:56,540 --> 00:26:57,300
Miss Chu,

476
00:27:02,180 --> 00:27:04,060
Mr. Wen asked me to congratulate you

477
00:27:04,060 --> 00:27:05,860
on your new store and factory launch

478
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:07,860
