00:27:23,500 --> 00:27:24,700
I've broken things off

486
00:27:24,940 --> 00:27:26,420
with your boss.

487
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:28,420
I don't need his congratulations,

488
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:29,780
nor his blessings.

489
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:31,620
So please,

490
00:27:31,940 --> 00:27:33,980
take it back.

491
00:27:34,420 --> 00:27:35,060
Thank you.

492
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:37,340
Miss Chu,

493
00:27:37,500 --> 00:27:39,180
