494
00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:40,260
I heard it is

495
00:27:40,260 --> 00:27:41,580
the most advanced in Shanghai.

496
00:27:41,900 --> 00:27:42,540
That's why

497
00:27:42,780 --> 00:27:44,180
we came.

498
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:44,700
Yes.

499
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:45,260
That's right.

500
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:47,340
I'll show you
around the factory in just a bit.

501
00:27:47,340 --> 00:27:49,420
But you've been waiting here
for so long

