504
00:27:51,820 --> 00:27:52,820
- Okay.
- Please.

505
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:53,620
Thank you.

506
00:27:53,620 --> 00:27:54,900
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

507
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:55,660
- Thank you.
- Congratulations.

