511
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:01,660
He and I are already strangers.

512
00:28:01,780 --> 00:28:02,940
How does that make me heartless?

513
00:28:03,060 --> 00:28:03,740
Thank you.

514
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:06,620
Everyone,

515
00:28:06,860 --> 00:28:08,820
our philosophy

516
00:28:09,140 --> 00:28:11,580
is to scientifically refine
and improve TCM.

517
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:14,340
Using our latest mechanical methods

518
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:16,500
to purify and extract TCM,

519
00:28:17,020 --> 00:28:18,940
we reprocess TCM in the style

520
00:28:19,060 --> 00:28:20,340
of Western medicine manufacturing.

521
00:28:22,180 --> 00:28:23,820
And these are

522
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:28,020
our upcoming products,

523
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:29,980
concentrated TCM pills,

524
00:28:30,460 --> 00:28:31,260
officially named Miracle Pills.

525
00:28:31,580 --> 00:28:34,700
Mechanical purification and extraction?

526
00:28:35,540 --> 00:28:36,620
What does that mean?

527
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:38,540
For the technical side of things,

528
00:28:38,540 --> 00:28:40,980
I'll defer to our chief engineer,

529
00:28:40,980 --> 00:28:42,140
Mr. Cheng Hui.

