00:29:59,780 --> 00:30:01,780
then opened branches
in Hong Kong, China, Shantou,

566
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:03,460
and Sanheba.

567
00:30:03,740 --> 00:30:04,980
I even heard he plans

568
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:06,900
to expand to Dapu, Yongding,

569
00:30:06,900 --> 00:30:07,980
Shanghang, and Tingzhou.

570
00:30:08,780 --> 00:30:09,860
Isn't that just ridiculous?

571
00:30:18,820 --> 00:30:19,980
Mr. Wen, she won't accept it.

572
00:30:20,660 --> 00:30:21,300
Just leave it there.

573
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:22,980
♪Your voice drifts to me,
never near, never far♪

574
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:28,660
♪Photo curled inside my worn wallet♪

575
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:34,700
♪Next year's journey awaits again♪

576
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:40,700
♪As seasons shift and fade♪

577
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:46,860
♪See the leaf fall at my toe♪

578
00:30:47,540 --> 00:30:52,500
♪Like time quietly slipping away♪

579
00:30:52,820 --> 00:30:57,940
♪And I couldn't quite understand♪

580
00:30:58,180 --> 00:31:04,540
♪Why are answers always silent?♪

581
00:31:04,540 --> 00:31:05,380
[Chichun Apothecary]

582
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:10,940
♪We walk through ordinary days♪

583
00:31:11,380 --> 00:31:16,980
♪What remains flows like rivers wide♪

584
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:22,020
♪Who will hold the tears
we used to hide?♪

585
00:31:22,260 --> 00:31:27,780
♪Each page turns, life's folded lines♪

586
00:31:28,220 --> 00:31:34,900
♪I may sigh through the rest of my life♪

587
00:31:35,220 --> 00:31:40,900
♪Yet my heart won't close its door♪

588
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:46,940
♪That fleeting light I failed to chase♪

589
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:50,740
♪Still lights each frame along my way♪

590
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:52,660
Chichun Apothecary is going all in
on Miracle Pill.

591
00:31:53,580 --> 00:31:54,500
I heard

592
00:31:54,620 --> 00:31:56,860
Shaohua's updated the ancient recipe

593
00:31:57,820 --> 00:32:00,100
and even used mechanical purification
and extraction technology.

594
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:02,020
Seems it works better than ever.

595
00:32:03,860 --> 00:32:06,340
Where'd she get the money

596
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:07,700
for such a massive factory?

597
00:32:09,340 --> 00:32:10,300
Wen Zhiqiu

598
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:13,700
bought back her shares at a steep price.

599
00:32:15,820 --> 00:32:16,700
I knew it.

600
00:32:17,940 --> 00:32:20,500
He still has feelings

601
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:21,700
for Chu Shaohua.

602
00:32:22,620 --> 00:32:23,860
Shaohua returned

603
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:26,340
the flower basket he sent.

604
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,620
That's something she would do.

605
00:32:32,140 --> 00:32:33,140
I'd say

606
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:37,340
Chu Shaohua is more of a go-getter
than Wen Zhiqiu.

607
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:43,300
Where did Wen Zhiqiu

608
00:32:44,340 --> 00:32:46,020
mess up this time?

609
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:50,420
He's totally finished.

610
00:32:51,380 --> 00:32:53,140
He used to be really smart.

611
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:56,060
His pharmacy ranked
among the top three in Shanghai.

612
00:32:57,340 --> 00:33:00,020
He made a mess of himself

613
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:03,020
and his business fell to pieces

614
00:33:03,340 --> 00:33:05,100
over that relationship.

615
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:07,900
So listen up,

616
00:33:08,580 --> 00:33:09,380
in business,

617
00:33:10,140 --> 00:33:11,860
you can't let emotions get in the way.

618
00:33:13,140 --> 00:33:15,100
Wen Zhiqiu is a cautionary tale.

619
00:33:15,580 --> 00:33:16,420
Got it.

620
00:33:24,140 --> 00:33:26,580
This is the new drug
I'm launching next month.

621
00:33:28,420 --> 00:33:30,340
I'm putting you

622
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,620
