623
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:40,140
You've been under my wing
for a while now.

624
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,100
Let's see what you've learned.

625
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:46,100
Okay.

626
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,340
I'm going to give it a try.

627
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:49,860
Try?

628
00:33:50,340 --> 00:33:52,060
From this moment on, every move you make

629
00:33:52,540 --> 00:33:54,060
has to be all or nothing.

630
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:55,300
Burn the boats.

631
00:33:57,580 --> 00:33:58,940
I understand.

632
00:34:00,740 --> 00:34:01,860
And let me remind you.

633
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:04,980
Its direct competitor

634
00:34:06,100 --> 00:34:07,260
is Miracle Pill.

635
00:34:10,660 --> 00:34:13,780
You're asking me
to go up against Shaohua?

636
00:34:13,780 --> 00:34:14,420
That's right.

637
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:17,100
No.

638
00:34:23,180 --> 00:34:24,620
Is there another option I can try?

639
00:34:25,940 --> 00:34:26,620
What's wrong?

640
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:30,660
Are you afraid you can't beat her?

641
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:32,420
No.

642
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:34,940
I'm afraid this is going

643
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:37,140
to affect my friendship with Shaohua.

644
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,660
Look at you.

645
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:40,940
I just told you

646
00:34:41,700 --> 00:34:43,020
to keep your emotions out of it.

647
00:34:43,380 --> 00:34:45,100
And you're letting your feelings
cloud your judgment once again.

648
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:46,540
But it's Shaohua.

649
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:51,900
Let me put it this way.

650
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:54,580
Once your interests clash,

651
00:34:54,980 --> 00:34:56,300
even if you show mercy,

652
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:59,140
Chu Shaohua won't back down.

653
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:03,020
She wouldn't do that.

654
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:04,980
Really?

655
00:35:06,780 --> 00:35:09,460
The way she treats Wen Zhiqiu now

656
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:11,140
is

657
00:35:11,340 --> 00:35:13,380
how she'll treat you down the line.

658
00:35:17,820 --> 00:35:18,620
So,

659
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,660
business and personal feelings

660
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:24,140
should remain separate.

661
00:35:25,740 --> 00:35:26,860
You really need

662
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:31,340
to learn from Chu Shaohua on this.

663
00:35:34,380 --> 00:35:35,900
And you know what, darling?

664
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:39,860
The only thing

665
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:41,980
that's pure in my world

666
00:35:42,860 --> 00:35:44,100
is money.

667
00:35:45,660 --> 00:35:48,140
So pure that it leaves no room
for distractions,

668
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:50,660
not even emotions.

669
00:35:52,140 --> 00:35:53,020
If you

670
00:35:54,140 --> 00:35:57,660
want to make big money,

671
00:35:58,660 --> 00:35:59,940
you'll have to let go

672
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:02,380
of a lot of emotional ties.

673
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:09,900
If it were someone else,
it would be fine.

674
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:13,500
But if it's Shaohua we're talking about,

675
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:16,820
I don't think I stand a chance.

676
00:36:20,100 --> 00:36:21,540
Don't be afraid, darling.

677
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:23,540
Think about it.

678
00:36:25,140 --> 00:36:26,340
Who's got your back?

679
00:36:33,060 --> 00:36:33,780
It's you,

680
00:36:35,980 --> 00:36:37,060
Shouyuan Apothecary,

681
00:36:38,380 --> 00:36:39,260
and Jujing Apothecary.

682
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:40,660
Precisely.

683
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:44,700
So, darling,

684
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:46,100
go all in and make it count.

685
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:51,860
That's how you truly show respect
for your opponent.

686
00:36:53,900 --> 00:36:54,540
Okay.

687
00:36:58,180 --> 00:36:58,860
I'll do it.

688
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:28,700
Bai.

689
00:37:31,540 --> 00:37:32,420
Sun?

690
00:37:32,780 --> 00:37:35,620
[Dongmeite Garden Apartment]

691
00:37:35,620 --> 00:37:36,540
Why are you back?

692
00:37:36,820 --> 00:37:37,980
Didn't you join the army?

693
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,300
How did you make it back so soon?

694
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:42,540
I joined the army

695
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:44,740
to fight the Japanese.

696
00:37:45,060 --> 00:37:46,820
But they sent us to Jiangxi

697
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:48,540
to go after the Chinese Communists.

698
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:51,700
I can't bring myself

699
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:54,180
to fight my own people.

700
00:38:00,780 --> 00:38:01,780
You doing okay?

701
00:38:06,700 --> 00:38:07,380
Yeah, I'm good.

702
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:09,700
Let's talk upstairs.

703
00:38:14,100 --> 00:38:14,740
Come on in.

704
00:38:26,700 --> 00:38:28,020
It's okay. Come in.

705
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:31,420
My...

706
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:33,820
My shoes are too dirty.

707
00:38:35,060 --> 00:38:35,900
It's alright.

708
00:38:36,020 --> 00:38:37,580
I'll grab you some clean clothes.

709
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:38,500
Take a shower,

710
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:39,660
then I'll treat you to something good.

711
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:43,020
Whose...?

712
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:47,940
I'm seeing someone.

713
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:52,740
He's probably loaded, right?

714
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:54,420
You know him.

715
00:38:54,940 --> 00:38:55,580
Xia Yuan.

716
00:39:01,340 --> 00:39:02,300
Xia Yuan?

717
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:04,380
I didn't expect it either.

718
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:08,980
Bai,

719
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:11,820
why would you do this to yourself?

720
00:39:13,820 --> 00:39:15,020
I couldn't help myself.

721
00:39:15,140 --> 00:39:16,300
Couldn't help yourself?

722
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:18,500
You had a choice.

723
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:20,980
You're perfectly capable
of making your own money,

724
00:39:21,620 --> 00:39:23,300
so why rely on men?

725
00:39:24,140 --> 00:39:25,460
What's wrong with that?

726
00:39:26,180 --> 00:39:27,900
Depending on men
is a kind of strength too.

727
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:29,500
You really are pathetic.

728
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:36,100
I don't care.

729
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:38,180
Bai,

730
00:39:38,580 --> 00:39:40,020
how could you turn out like this?

731
00:39:40,500 --> 00:39:41,500
That's just who I am.

732
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,900
I'm shameless.

733
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:46,660
Yes, I rely on men.

734
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:47,260
So what?

735
00:39:47,540 --> 00:39:49,340
What gives you the right to judge me?

736
00:39:49,540 --> 00:39:51,300
Where were you when I needed you?

737
00:39:51,540 --> 00:39:52,860
My restaurant was bombed,

738
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:54,580
and I was trapped under the rubble,

739
00:39:54,580 --> 00:39:55,820
barely clinging to life.

740
00:39:55,980 --> 00:39:56,820
Where were you then?

741
00:39:56,980 --> 00:39:58,140
I was serving our country!

742
00:39:58,260 --> 00:39:59,300
Then why are the Japanese

743
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:00,220
still parading around in China?

744
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,420
As a soldier,

745
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,380
you failed to protect the nation.

746
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:03,300
As a man,

747
00:40:03,300 --> 00:40:04,740
you failed to protect
the woman you love.

748
00:40:05,140 --> 00:40:06,220
And you still look down on me?

749
00:40:06,740 --> 00:40:07,860
You're in no position to judge!

750
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:48,060
[Shanghai Shaohua Pharmaceuticals]

751
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:49,580
What's going on?

752
00:40:50,060 --> 00:40:50,900
Miracle Pill

753
00:40:51,100 --> 00:40:52,660
has met a serious challenger.

754
00:40:53,140 --> 00:40:53,660
What is it?

755
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:58,500
Jujing Apothecary
just introduced the Yushu Pill.

756
00:41:01,420 --> 00:41:02,700
Its ingredients are similar
to Miracle Pill.

757
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:04,420
We ran tests.

758
00:41:04,620 --> 00:41:06,340
Its efficacy is far inferior,

759
00:41:07,100 --> 00:41:09,060
but its sales are ten times higher.

760
00:41:09,220 --> 00:41:09,900
Our sales

761
00:41:09,980 --> 00:41:12,020
have taken a big hit because of this.

762
00:41:13,140 --> 00:41:14,500
Tell me how they did it.

763
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:15,980
Their pricing is lower than ours.

764
00:41:16,260 --> 00:41:18,620
And the rebates and payment terms
they offer to apothecaries

765
00:41:18,620 --> 00:41:19,340
are extremely generous.

766
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:20,940
If it were just those two things,

767
00:41:20,980 --> 00:41:22,580
we wouldn't be afraid to compete.

768
00:41:23,020 --> 00:41:24,020
But what's truly infuriating

769
00:41:24,660 --> 00:41:25,900
is that they're throwing
huge sums of money around,

770
00:41:26,180 --> 00:41:28,420
locking in exclusive deals
with apothecaries.

771
00:41:28,900 --> 00:41:31,140
Selling Yushu means
Miracle Pill is out of the picture.

772
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:33,900
But how is this strategy
making them any money?

773
00:41:34,500 --> 00:41:35,780
They don't care about making money.

774
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:37,100
They just want to crush us.

775
00:41:37,260 --> 00:41:40,500
I heard that this wasn't
even Xia Yuan's idea.

776
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:41,740
It's

777
00:41:42,740 --> 00:41:43,500
a Miss Bai.

778
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:55,260
A cup of coffee, please.

779
00:41:58,020 --> 00:41:58,860
Miss Bai.

780
00:42:00,220 --> 00:42:00,900
Ms. Chu.

781
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:03,100
What's the rush

782
00:42:03,700 --> 00:42:04,540
to see me?

783
00:42:05,900 --> 00:42:07,780
Yushu Pill

784
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:09,940
has been a big hit lately.

785
00:42:12,980 --> 00:42:13,660
I heard.

786
00:42:14,060 --> 00:42:14,900
You're good.

787
00:42:15,540 --> 00:42:17,740
You're trying to put me
out of business, aren't you?

788
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:22,860
Thank you.

789
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:26,300
Not really.

790
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:29,020
This is my first performance report

791
00:42:29,020 --> 00:42:30,500
