792
00:42:30,700 --> 00:42:32,540
Guess I just went a little overboard.

793
00:42:33,100 --> 00:42:34,980
Did Xia Yuan tell you to do this?

794
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:37,140
It was also my idea.

795
00:42:37,380 --> 00:42:38,700
Aren't you worried

796
00:42:39,580 --> 00:42:41,420
