797
00:42:44,620 --> 00:42:46,700
I was, at first.

798
00:42:49,060 --> 00:42:50,500
But then I realized

799
00:42:51,220 --> 00:42:52,540
business and personal feelings

800
00:42:52,660 --> 00:42:53,620
should stay separate.

801
00:42:55,580 --> 00:42:57,020
Did Xia Yuan teach you that too?

